      "role": "user",
      "content": "alchemy? lol i guess haha. but yeah, you mentioned it's between amino acids and sugars. does that mean if i change the type of flour or maybe add more sugar to the dough it'll happen faster? i'm trying to get a really dark crust without it tasting bitter.",
